                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="feature-icon">👁️‍🗨️</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Your Eyes Only</strong> — Private articles are completely 
                        hidden from other world members
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="feature-icon">🔐</span>
                    <div>
